.TH simple_shell 1 "January 2026"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple UNIX command line interpreter
.SH SYNOPSIS
simple_shell
.SH DESCRIPTION
A simple shell that reads commands from the user, executes them, and displays a prompt. Supports only single-word commands. Handles errors and Ctrl+D (EOF).
.SH USAGE
Run with:
$ ./hsh
Then type commands like /bin/ls, /bin/pwd, etc.
